sub_title: State Councillor in the Advisory Division of the Dutch Council of State
summary: Sigrid Hemels is State Councillor in the Advisory Division of the Dutch Council of State. In addition, she is professor of tax law at the Erasmus School of Law (ESL) of the Erasmus University Rotterdam and visiting professor in tax law at the Lund University School of Economics and Management. She has published and lectured, both in the Netherlands and abroad, on various topics including tax incentives for charities and the arts, exchange of information and European tax law.
